es such as Multi-Stakeholder Platforms (MSPs) and consensus building, and finally focuses on the diversity of agreements which can be produced to regulate or encourage fairer and more effective water allocation and use. About IUCN IUCN, International Union for Conservation of Nature, helps the world find pragmatic solutions to our most pressing environment and development challenges.", "start_char_idx": null, "end_char_idx": null, "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_seperator": "\n"}, "__type__": "1"}, "7300a42c-dba2-481a-b19a-ad603f626fbc": {"__data__": {"id_": "7300a42c-dba2-481a-b19a-ad603f626fbc", "embedding": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/iucn-ramsar-collaboration-supporting-wise-use-wetlands", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "IUCN - Ramsar collaboration : supporting the wise use of wetlands", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/iucn-ramsar-collaboration-supporting-wise-use-wetlands", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "12f6f85990152ec0a94d4226ba3f5428842505205d2508e325fc6a01b281735c"}, "2": {"node_id": "251fd76a-2ec1-49ee-b282-46f9fc2278c9", "node_type": null, "metadata": {"Title_URL": "https://www.iucn.org/resources/grey-literature/iucn-ramsar-collaboration-supporting-wise-use-wetlands", "Author": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Publisher": "International Union for Conservation of Nature", "Type": "Report"}, "hash": "ed575b1b9d55f1ceebf4109f43c08afd94708fa40cfb6325e3bd1d7682eaadf2"}}, "hash": "f328b0c6caf6b4cee4b86a6c116f9b317da2dde8da4760dbbefd91775e8